quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  34,1,"Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye bikwiye Allah, we ugenga ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi. Kandi ni we ukwiye ibisingizo byuzuye ku mperuka; ndetse ni we Ushishoza, Umumenyi wa byose"
  34,2,"Azi ibyinjira mu butaka n’ibibusohokamo, ibimanuka mu kirere ndetse n’ibikizamukamo. Kandi ni Nyirimbabazi, Nyirimpuhwe"
  34,3,"Babandi bahakanye baravuze bati \"Imperuka ntizatugeraho\". Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ndahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani wanjye, Umumenyi w’ibitagaragara, ko rwose izabageraho (nta kabuza); nta kimwisoba mu birere cyangwa mu isi kabone n’iyo cyaba kingana n’impeke y’ururo cyangwa kiri mu nsi yacyo ndetse n’ikinini kuri cyo, usibye ko (byose) biri mu gitabo gisobanutse"
  34,4,(Ibyo ni) ukugira ngo (Allah) azagororere babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza. Abo bazababarirwa ibyaha ndetse banahabwe amafunguro yubahitse
  34,5,"Naho babandi baharaniye gutesha agaciro amagambo yacu (bibwira ko) bazadutsinda, bazahanishwa ibihano bibi cyane kandi bibabaza"
  34,6,"Na babandi bahawe ubumenyi bw’ibyo wahishuriwe (wowe Muhamadi) biturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe, (babona ko) ari ukuri kandi ko biyobora biganisha mu nzira y’Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Usingizwa cyane"
  34,7,"Naho babandi bahakanye baravuze bati \"Ese tubereke umuntu (Muhamadi) ubabwira ko (nimuramuka mupfuye, imibiri yanyu) igashwanyagurika ikaba ubushingwe, ko rwose (nta gushidikanya, muzongera) mukaremwa bundi bushya"